# Context

This glossary is the shared language for the repo.

## How To Use This File

- Add terms when the team settles on a meaning that code, tests, and docs should share.
- Prefer updating an existing term over inventing a near-duplicate.
- Link to ADRs when a term depends on a specific architectural decision.

## Terms

### Walking Skeleton

The smallest end-to-end slice that proves the project boots, its main workflow runs, and at least one real test passes.
